Comparing the 7-day averages of daily confirmed cases from the past 7 days and those from 8-14 days ago, case counts have increased by 3.9%, while daily reported deaths have increased by 6.8%. Similar comparative 7-day averages in the USA show a 14.7% decrease in daily reported cases and 4.9% decrease in reported deaths.

